article.description: O'Showen Williams registered 19 points as Appalachian State beat Charlotte 64-55 on Thursday night.
article.headline: Williams carries Appalachian St. past Charlotte 64-55
article.linkText: Williams carries Appalachian St. past Charlotte 64-55
article.story: BOONE, N.C. -- O'Showen Williams registered 19 points as Appalachian State beat Charlotte 64-55 on Thursday night. Adrian Delph had 15 points for Appalachian State (4-3). Jordan Shepherd scored a career-high 20 points for the 49ers (2-2). Appalachian State matches up against East Tennessee State on the road on Tuesday. Charlotte takes on Georgia State on the road on Wednesday. --- More AP college basketball: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and https://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
